ik kan laksen bli enda sunnere"}, {"field": "url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/2016/04/24/Omega-3-i-laks-fra-ny-plante-12636320.ece"}, {"field": "urlhash", "value": "9c2084371cf86ba614b9802c304ff07875ae5c90"}], "score": 0.4951581, "siteId": "9222270286501375973", "id": "9c2084371cf86ba614b9802c304ff07875ae5c90"}

